  "description": "Expose explicit start-directory bootstrap through openSpecdHost so SDK hosts can discover projects from a chosen root without mutating process.cwd() or forcing a specd.yaml path. The SDK contract now distinguishes configPath from startDir, rejects mixed bootstrap inputs up front, and keeps existing configPath and default-cwd behavior intact. The change also aligns tests and public docs with the new host bootstrap semantics.",
